*Oblasti* su postale sve popularnije među turistima. (Areas have become increasingly popular among tourists.)

Uglavnom se posmatraju dve glavne *oblasti* u kojima se obrazovanje razlikuje. (Generally two main areas are observed in which education differs.)

U nastojanju da poboljša obrazovanje u *oblasti* matematike, Ministarstvo obrazovanja je donelo nova pravila. (In an effort to improve education in the field of mathematics, the Ministry of Education has introduced new regulations.)

Mnogi stručnjaci su se usredsredili na istraživanje te *oblasti*. (Many experts have focused on researching that area.)

*Oblasti* se mogu podeliti na tri kategorije. (Areas can be divided into three categories.)